test_list_of_several_same_number:
assert [[]] == [[-779], [-779]]
  At index 0 diff: [] != [-779]
  Right contains one more item: [-779]
  Full diff:
  - [[-779], [-779]]
  + [[]]
test_if_sublist_product_equals_number:
assert 19 == -779
 +  where 19 = <built-in function prod>([-1, -19])
 +    where <built-in function prod> = math.prod
